    <string name="help_content">FAQ\n\n1. Low accuracy?\n- Ensure clothing fills the frame\n- Try Crop or Enhance reclassify\n- Improve lighting\n\n2. Permissions\n- Camera: photo recognition\n- Storage: gallery and local export\n\n3. Batch classify\n- Use Batch Classify on Classify tab\n\n4. Backup\n- Local ZIP/JSONL only in Export Data; no cloud account sync\n\nTips\n- Flat lay or hanger shots work best\n- Avoid busy backgrounds\n- Single item should cover 60%%+ of frame</string>
